title: Blitzcranks pull stopping half way through pulls
body: I had a few bot games messing around recently and i noticed a few times when i pulled the taric and warwick bots that they didnt come all they way too me , they would stop half way through the pull , and they were just bots so it wasnt cleanse or any item that would sheild it , sorry i dont have a link or a picture of it but hopefully this helps! would be annoying in ranked play!
